I play a mage (its actually my main) and I am getting sick of hear this constant whinning about "ohhh, he/she can do this, we need that or we are worthless".  This is bull%#@*!!!!  <P>1)  NUKES<BR>We are 2nd in over all DD damage to wizards with Druids close behind us BUT remember to add in our pets.  They are after all an extension of us.  DD stands for Direct Damage and our pets damage is also DIrect Damage.  So with our Shocks and Bolts added with our pets melee we are just about equal to Wizards in "Direct Damage" especially mana wise.<P>2)  PETS<BR>Why is it when ever a new class or race comes out EVERYONE is crying about who gets what before its even in Gold stage??  This is plain childish!!!  So what if Beastmasters get a pet at 9th level.  I do not hear you crying about ShadowKnights and they get pets at 9th (sorry SKs if this starts a flame on your pets).  As for our pets not being as powerful or what erver BS is flying around, its just that BS!!  Our pets will on any day stomp anyother pet of equal level because our DS and buffs and summoned weapons give us a edge.  Just ask any Necro who will tell you the truth and they will tell you that in a 39th Skele and 39th Earth pet fight the Earth will tromp (personally I use Water) the Skele.  And no Necros I am NOT trying to say you are weak, I am just stating a factual point.<P>3)  BEASTLORD<BR>Lets WAIT and see what actually is done with this when its done with BETA and is in GOLD phase.  Any information that is out now is strictly speculation and rumors.  NOTHING IS FINAL!!!<P>4)  SPELLS<BR>Our summon spells are VERY useful to eanyone and everyone from 1 - 60.  I have been asked several times for bandages, weapons (for pets), waterstones, etc. So our spells are not useless.  I will agree that we could use a few more summoned weapons with procs if at all possible.<P>5)  MANA REGEN<BR>I to would like a mana regen ability that cost less HP loss then what we have (Mod Rods) but look at the Shaman (I have a shaman too).  Their so call mana regen spell SUCKS until higher levels.  I personally have Canabolized 3 bubbles of HP for less then HALF a bubble of mana.  Now if you ask me, the Mod Rod looks ALOT better then that.  And as for the casting cost being about equal to the amount of mana it gives you, I look at this and like a piggy bank of mana.  You cast it, put it away for a rainy day and med back to FM.  Then when you need extra mana, BANG you have it.  So whats the problem.<P>6) ESCAPE<BR>This is true, without a speed augmentaion item (J-Boots) or SoW we must hope out pet is able to keep the nasties off of us long enough to gate but this is a double edged sword.  If you are soloing you understand the risks involved AND if you do not know by now when to start casting gate to be out of danger before Goner is dead then you need to pick another class or stop buying your characters on EBay.<P>Now I know alot of you mages out there are going to want to FLAME ME and all I have to say is go ahead, it will just prove my point that those complaining the most are the most immature of us.  Sure the mage class has its ups and downs but as a whole I would not trade being a mage for all the plat in Norrath!!!<P>And if you think me a noob (or any other immature term you have) let me point out I have been playing EQ since Day 1 when it went public and think I know a bit about the class.<P>Thank you for your time my fellow mages.<P>Zaymot Silver<BR>40th Summoner of Fennin Ro<BR>Order of the Wolf<P>P.S. If you are wondering how a mage that has been playing since the start of EQ can only be 40th let me explain.  I got my first mage to 38th then deleted him.  got my next one to 20th and deleted him, my next one to 35th and deleted him and then took a break and after a while of playing a SK, Shaman, Druid, Warrior, Wizard, Enchanter & Monk I started this Mage and have now gotten him to 40th and will be 41st this weekend.  So as you see, besides have a good amount of knowledge of the mage I have sampled the other classes too and know a little of what I am talking about.  I guess the most I can expect you all to get out of this post is this....<P>Do not judge other character/classes by their abilities seperately but as a whole and NEVER judge a character/class/ability/etc that DOES NOT even exsist yet on the live server.<P>Sorry this got so long.  Hope to see you all later.
